.TH REVIEW_ARTIST_IDENTITY_TUI 1 "2026-03-29" "stophammer" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
review_artist_identity_tui \- interactive review console for pending artist identity items
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B review_artist_identity_tui
[
.BI --db " PATH"
] [
.BI --limit " N"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B review_artist_identity_tui
opens a terminal UI for feed-scoped artist identity review items produced by
the resolver. It is intended for operators who need to inspect evidence and
store durable merge or reject decisions interactively.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --db " PATH"
Path to the SQLite database. Defaults to
.BR ./stophammer.db .
.TP
.BI --limit " N"
Maximum number of pending review items to load. Defaults to 200.
.SH CONTROLS
The interface shows the pending review list, the competing artist candidates,
and feed evidence. Use the on-screen key hints to move focus, inspect evidence,
reload the queue, and store decisions.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Open the TUI against the default database:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db
.fi
.TP
Limit the initial queue size:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_artist_identity_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db --limit 100
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR review_artist_identity (1),
.BR backfill_artist_identity (1),
.BR stophammer-resolverd (1)
